%F A156996 From _G. C. Greubel_, May 14 2021: (Start)
%F A156996 T(n, 0) = A000179(n).
%F A156996 T(n, k) = Sum_{j=k..n} (-1)^(j+k)*(2*n*(n-j)!/(2*n-j))*binomial(j, k)*binomial(2*n-j, j), with T(0, k) = 1. (End)
